          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-archive-1620750629788-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are done, stir the<strong> soft cheese</strong> through the soup and blitz until smooth with a <strong>(stick) blender</strong></p><p>Stir the<strong> reserved leeks</strong> through the soup and season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>leek & potato soup</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of boiled water if the soup is looking a little thick!</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
